    <abstract>
      <t>[I-D.ietf-detnet-scaling-requirements] proposed the data plane requirements in scaling networks. This document describes the specific requirements for flow aggregation in enhanced DetNet and provides the enhancement considerations. It also discusses how the flow aggregation could be realized in a 5GS logical DetNet node participating in enhanced DetNet.</t>
